<Layout title="Research" description="Research by Christina M. Bradley — publications, awards, and talks">
  <div class="research-page">
    <h1>Research</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      My research focuses on (1) how individuals respond to the emotions of others and (2) how
      individuals express emotions in ways that enhance individual, relational, and team
      effectiveness. I am especially interested in emotion responding and expression in challenging
      situations, such as conflict and hierarchy.
    </p>

