          Responding to the Emotions of Others at Work: A Review and Integrative Theoretical
          Framework for the Effects of Emotion-Response Strategies on Work-Related Outcomes.
          <em>Academy of Management Annals</em>, 18(1), 3–43.
        </p>
        <p class="pub-note">
          Featured in a showcase symposium at the Academy of Management organized by authors (2023)
